\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec2 Now we just read what God actually said..is that what He said? \'a0No\'85but that is the narrative twist. \'a0To put doubt in our minds and pain God as someone who is\'a0withholding from you\'85and it works.\uc0\u8232 \
