\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec2 Alcohol is a great example\'85.God says don\'92t get drunk\'85many christians are like don\'92t drink it.\uc0\u8232 \
\ls4\ilvl1\kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 {\listtext	\uc0\u9702 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec2 Is that what God says\'85no that is the spirit of eve coming out in all of us.\uc0\u8232 \
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\partightenfactor0
\ls4\ilvl0\cf2 \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec2 The second thing is there is yet another subtle thing she left out in the wording\'85it goes from they will certainly die to just die.\uc0\u8232 \
\pard\tx940\tx1440\pardeftab720\li1440\fi-1440\partightenfactor0
\ls4\ilvl1\cf2 \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 {\listtext	\uc0\u9702 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec2 It\'92s small\'85but when you put all three together what you get is this step away from God and into religion and rules.\uc0\u8232 \
\ls4\ilvl1\kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 {\listtext	\uc0\u9702 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec2 A step into lessoning our freedoms and enjoying all that God has given to us and a step toward rule following and regulations\uc0\u8232 \
\ls4\ilvl1\kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 {\listtext	\uc0\u9702 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec2 Ultimately this is a step toward God and it happened before she bit into the apple. \'a0\uc0\u8232 \
