\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec2 \'a0I mean come on, isn\'92t God just this mean controlling cosmic killjoy that wants to manipulate the masses and make sure you are oppressed? \'a0Isn\'92t He holding out on you, keeping the best things from you\'85I mean isn\'92t God ultimately\'85the enemy of our freedom? \'a0\cf5 \strokec5 \
